WEBVTT

1
00:00:15.280 --> 00:00:18.300
Chen Dashao, long time no see Mr. Xue

2
00:00:18.440 --> 00:00:19.380
Can we talk?

3
00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:21.040
Mr. Chen is polite

4
00:00:21.040 --> 00:00:21.980
Certainly!

5
00:00:22.440 --> 00:00:24.020
So I'm going to cut to the chase.

6
00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:28.460
I want to know what the relationship between the black gold group and the empress of Beijing is

7
00:00:29.920 --> 00:00:32.660
Sorry, even if you are the eldest of the family

8
00:00:33.040 --> 00:00:35.480
I can't answer you this question either.

9
00:00:35.480 --> 00:00:38.820
But I'm sure you'll know the answer soon

10
00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:52.280
Why did your brother marry Mr. Chen?

11
00:00:52.280 --> 00:00:56.140
However, Master Chen obviously doesn't know your brother's true identity

12
00:00:58.760 --> 00:01:00.540
If I'm not mistaken

13
00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:05.580
This woman is the wife of a department manager at my black gold syndicate

14
00:01:05.760 --> 00:01:08.460
How could I care whose wife he used to be?

15
00:01:08.560 --> 00:01:10.180
But now he's mine

16
00:01:10.280 --> 00:01:13.300
You may or may not listen to what I say next

17
00:01:13.640 --> 00:01:15.660
The empress of Beijing owes me a favor

18
00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:17.140
Now I want to pay it back

19
00:01:18.120 --> 00:01:19.980
I need him when I need him

20
00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:22.020
He can protect me

21
00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:25.700
If there's nothing else, I'll take my leave

22
00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:27.900
What is Mengxi still waiting for?

